description: Local Boys Shave Ice is serving the streets of maui. They make their own ice, azuki beans, syrup flavors, and world famous kauai cream.  Local Boys uses Roselani ice cream and soft rice mochi.  Not only are they known for making the #1 shave ice in Hawaii, but they also serve jumbo beef hot dogs, local favorite chili and rice, ice cream and real fruit smoothies!
name: Local Boy's Shave Ice
